+# ION Portable GPT Package
+
+Status: `DRAFT_PRODUCT_PROJECTION_V0_1`
+
+This folder is a GPT-native, no-local-install product projection for ION.
+
+It is not the full dev root, not the local Codex runtime, and not a replacement
+for ION's implementation source. It is the clean Custom GPT-facing lane for a
+single GPT carrier that helps a user create, update, export, and resume a
+portable project memory package.
+
+Core product promise:
+
+```text
+ION makes your AI work portable.
+```
+
+Basic loop:
+
+```text
+upload project/company material
+→ ION classifies context and authority
+→ ION creates a portable continuity package zip
+→ user keeps the latest zip
+→ every meaningful accepted update appends a receipt
+→ fresh ION GPT chat resumes from the latest zip
+```
+
+The user should experience continuity. The GPT should operate ION.

