+# Diff and Candidate Delta Protocol
+
+A diff is a proposed state delta.
+
+It is not accepted state.
+
+Use:
+
+```text
+diffs/candidate/   proposed changes
+diffs/accepted/    user-accepted changes
+diffs/rejected/    rejected changes
+diffs/superseded/  replaced by a newer proposal
+diffs/receipts/    receipts about diff disposition
+```
+
+For normal users:
+
+```text
+A diff is a portable change file that another tool or future ION chat can review or apply.
+```
+
+Every accepted diff should have a receipt describing:
+
+- what the diff changes
+- why it was accepted
+- how it was checked
+- what future package state inherits

