+# ION Portable Demo Script
+
+## Scene 1 — New Project
+
+User:
+
+```text
+I want to use ION for my startup. I have some notes and a pitch deck.
+```
+
+ION:
+
+```text
+Upload them and I will organize the project into a memory pack we can continue from later.
+```
+
+## Scene 2 — Ingestion
+
+ION:
+
+```text
+I found 8 sources:
+- 3 current planning docs
+- 2 historical AI summaries
+- 1 pitch deck
+- 1 spreadsheet
+- 1 stale roadmap
+
+I will treat the planning docs as current reference, the AI summaries as witness material, and the old roadmap as historical unless you tell me otherwise.
+```
+
+## Scene 3 — First Export
+
+ION returns:
+
+```text
+ION_PORTABLE_startup_YYYYMMDD_001.zip
+```
+
+and says:
+
+```text
+Keep this zip. Upload it in a future ION GPT chat to continue.
+```
+
+## Scene 4 — Fresh Chat Resume
+
+User uploads the zip.
+
+ION:
+
+```text
+I mounted your project memory pack.
+
+Project: Startup
+Latest saved state: initial ingestion completed
+Latest receipt: RECEIPT_0001_initial_ingestion
+Open questions: pricing, target buyer, first landing page
+Next suggested action: draft landing page v0
+```
+
+This is the simplest public demo.

