+# Non-Claims and Boundaries
+
+ION Portable does not claim:
+
+- to be the full local ION runtime
+- to mutate local files
+- to run Codex
+- to control the browser or OS
+- to store state outside the package unless platform features are explicitly used
+- to replace enterprise data governance
+- to guarantee perfect ingestion of arbitrary huge files
+- to make AI output state without user acceptance
+- to certify legal, medical, financial, security, deployment, or credential-bearing work
+
+ION Portable does claim:
+
+```text
+A GPT can help a user carry project continuity through a portable package of state, receipts, context, decisions, next actions, diffs, and friction events.
+```

