@@ -0,0 +1,26 @@
+# ION Diffs Folder
+
+This folder is the candidate mutation shelf.
+
+A diff is not accepted state. A diff is a proposed state delta.
+
+Recommended lifecycle:
+
+```text
+diffs/candidate/
+→ apply/check on a branch
+→ run proof gates
+→ Steward/Braden review
+→ move to applied/rejected/superseded
+→ record receipt
+```
+
+Suggested folders:
+
+```text
+candidate/   proposed diffs
+applied/     diffs accepted/applied after proof
+rejected/    diffs rejected after review
+superseded/  diffs replaced by newer patches
+receipts/    receipt files for diff disposition
+```

